//*           programs to encrypt and decrypt your data using       *   FILE 618
//*           IBM's ICSF Cryptographic Services Facility.           *   FILE 618
//*                                                                 *   FILE 618
//*           email:  "Pergentino Arias" <pergen@mixmail.com>       *   FILE 618
